  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/cbb10ed198bb0368d299cd92cdacd279.avif?t=1767641013\" width=780 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the thrilling era of the Crusades and forge your destiny in <i>Knights of the Crusades</i>. Combining real-time strategy, city-building, and sandbox gameplay, this immersive experience lets you rewrite history and lead a knightly order to glory. Will you rise as a beacon of faith, or succumb to the challenges of a war-torn world?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/e81d2a653839db92258b847202c0569a.poster.avif?t=1767641013\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/e81d2a653839db92258b847202c0569a.webm?t=1767641013\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/e81d2a653839db92258b847202c0569a.mp4?t=1767641013\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/63ae5d92f02e321d148521cfc054b0a0.avif?t=1767641013\" width=780 height=100 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Begin your adventure as a founding member of the legendary Templars or your custom Holy Order</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel from Western Europe to the Holy Land to take part in the First Crusades</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a founding father of the Holy Order</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/b461832b59a79ef48b43ae6913ec61f5.avif?t=1767641013\" width=780 height=100 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Capture and develop hamlets with dozens of essential structures </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate complex economy system with survival elements both in RTS and World Map modes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Generate resources like silver and piety, which are critical for expanding your influence and sustaining your armies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/59d6ed395b70d37a47ff31026b938367.poster.avif?t=1767641013\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/59d6ed395b70d37a47ff31026b938367.webm?t=1767641013\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/59d6ed395b70d37a47ff31026b938367.mp4?t=1767641013\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/e99f626d13d3e40fec2848e7975f65df.avif?t=1767641013\" width=780 height=100 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in epic RTS combat against AI armies on land and at sea.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defend your hamlets, siege massive cities, and rewrite history through challenging scripted scenarios.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/7e188432f7d14aefc6de6cbe97f0da1e.poster.avif?t=1767641013\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/7e188432f7d14aefc6de6cbe97f0da1e.webm?t=1767641013\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/7e188432f7d14aefc6de6cbe97f0da1e.mp4?t=1767641013\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/1b9c6f9957c435e844c78c5ba6243274.avif?t=1767641013\" width=780 height=100 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transition into open-ended gameplay after the main campaign, capturing new territories and building alliances</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience escalating challenges with Muslim, Slavic, and Christian AI factions vying for control of key regions</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/55db64aa53e91ccca3c86a0b2af63eed.avif?t=1767641013\" width=780 height=80 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lead campaigns in the Holy Land, Spain, North Africa, and Eastern Europe. Use strategy and diplomacy to secure alliances or crush your foes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Participate in historical events, like the Reconquista or the defense of Edessa, and determine the fate of the Holy Land.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/ef6279c97e82a476a81d6f53615ab44f.poster.avif?t=1767641013\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/ef6279c97e82a476a81d6f53615ab44f.webm?t=1767641013\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/ef6279c97e82a476a81d6f53615ab44f.mp4?t=1767641013\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/9af7e61b7aee814be1e4c7d2d884fef5.avif?t=1767641013\" width=780 height=100 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a massive map filled with towns, cities, and pilgrim routes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate dynamic events, including naval battles, sieges, and AI faction wars.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face challenges such as piety-driven resource systems, excommunication events, and escalating enemy attacks.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/53d0f754b9220383db8832894ea73b0f.poster.avif?t=1767641013\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/53d0f754b9220383db8832894ea73b0f.webm?t=1767641013\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/53d0f754b9220383db8832894ea73b0f.mp4?t=1767641013\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you rise to the challenge, expand your knightly order, and safeguard the future of Christendom? <i>Knights of the Crusades</i> invites you to embark on a grand journey of strategy, faith, and conquest.</p>",
